{"tid":213009,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"晚清時期青樓女子的工作","createTime":"2017-04-22T21:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T12:16:26.000Z","uid":58099,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f54a0e9effde6b707f951da65f2a384f6ae8ced","tid":213009,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T21:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/t6225201704209945g63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Ft6225201704209945g63.jpg&h=3ee23e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為了活命，青樓女不得不見人說人話見鬼說鬼話，在達官顯貴、軍警憲特、地痞無賴這些三教九流中周旋，因此，青樓中形成很多富有特殊意義的專用詞彙，而且保留至今，只是意思已完全改變。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/f46948201704209945w63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Ff46948201704209945w63.jpg&h=af2e6237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n彈琵琶的陪酒女，看上去就像未成年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/x46606201704209945i63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fx46606201704209945i63.jpg&h=e32b2406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港歌妓。開盤：在舊時青樓里，「開盤」指客人讓女子陪着聊天、唱曲，不包括不堪入目的活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/p40286201704209945f63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fp40286201704209945f63.jpg&h=09e13c97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這種雕刻華麗裝飾花哨的「花船」，實際上是水上青樓。調頭：指青樓女從原來的青樓轉到另一青樓中營業，猶如現代人換工作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/p14392201704209945l63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fp14392201704209945l63.jpg&h=1f681e3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上海福州路一雛妓出台時的情景。晚清上海青樓界慣例，為破身的雛妓（稱「清倌人」）應局，需有「龜奴」肩負。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/b3685201704209945b63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fb3685201704209945b63.jpg&h=07e48992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n和嫖客一起吸食鴉片。出局：指嫖客花錢把女子接出青樓，送到自己家裏或者其他隱祕的地方過夜，招她們「出局」須開「局票」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/k38981201704209945z63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fk38981201704209945z63.jpg&h=c8feb59e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與嫖客合奏一曲。開方子：「開方子」指青樓女通過察言觀色，裝可憐的方式以及各種藉口向嫖客敲詐的手段。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/u19891201704209945x63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fu19891201704209945x63.jpg&h=c1ec37e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上海尚仁里的青樓女李金鳳。1904年獲得《繁華報》花榜第三名，從此艷名大播。跳槽：指嫖客拋棄原來的女子另結新歡。花錢享樂的嫖客，個個喜新厭舊。<br />\n<br />\n古代青樓裏面的三種從業人員：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/w50427201704209945a63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fw50427201704209945a63.jpg&h=7a26b93f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一種是青樓經營者:老鴇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/x34783201704209945d63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fx34783201704209945d63.jpg&h=3de345a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在盛世裏面，生意好做，但是要是在亂世，比如在元明清，朝代更替的時候，作為經營者她們是不好做的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/n2031201704209945t63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fn2031201704209945t63.jpg&h=881e3bc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一方面要付工資，另一方面要交稅，歷朝歷代，都是由專門的稅收，明朝時期，最為明顯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/r46928201704209945k63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fr46928201704209945k63.jpg&h=3f0974a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老鴇有兩種經營模式，一種是固定場所，租房子，另外一種是遊動式的，，沒有門面，利用花船之類的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/r31946201704209945h63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fr31946201704209945h63.jpg&h=8366910a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二種是：青樓的員工&mdash;&mdash;仆傭。在明末清初小說《醒世姻緣傳》裏面有一段記載，青樓仆傭討工錢的事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/z28087201704209945x63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fz28087201704209945x63.jpg&h=dc2723ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廚子、賬房先生、雜役是一類，按月領取工資。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/v37452201704209945n63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fv37452201704209945n63.jpg&h=4435457e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n娘姨、貼身丫鬟是一類，她們是要應酬場面的，從利潤裏面分成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/f1097201704209945e63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Ff1097201704209945e63.jpg&h=965b68a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三種：核心人員&mdash;&mdash;青樓女子。青樓的財富之源,其他從業者賴以生存的基礎。這些女子的來源不一樣，培養方式也不一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/s54228201704209945w63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fs54228201704209945w63.jpg&h=610e9d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個芳名遠播的核心人員，可以撐起一整個門面。利潤也當然會源源不斷，最受青樓老闆器重。"},{"pid":"62f0e5b85f484fc97a39838f3dd4d7eca386747e","tid":213009,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T22:28:58.000Z","msg":"古時做雞辛苦好多"},{"pid":"9a87eaa75541517554db1677db14119422752bd4","tid":213009,"uid":5954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T22:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj